# NAS-AI Redesign Tracker

## Ground Rules
- One step at a time. Discuss → agree → implement.
- No hardcoding in code or config files.
- Every change is covered by a smoke test before and after.
- GitHub commit after each completed step.
- Breaking something while fixing something else = rollback immediately.

